have been more convenient to hold the ceremony in Tijuana.
</P>
<P>
   Fox's election came one day after the moment when whites
officially became a minority in California. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (75-WORD OPTIONAL TRIM BEGINS HERE AT 300) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   Nothing represents the growing domestic significance of Mexico
better than the family history of the Bushes.
</P>
<P>
   Prescott Bush, a senator from Connecticut, epitomized the
Waspish traditions of the Eastern Seaboard. George Bush began the
