out towards Mexico.
</P>
<P>
   His nephew, George P. Bush, whose mother is Mexican and who
speaks fluent Spanish, represents the next stage. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (END OF OPTIONAL TRIM. STORY CONTINUES TO 1,050) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   Of course, Mexico's significance in American domestic politics
