in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
 &HT;    
 From The Economist magazine  
 c.2000 Economist Newspaper Ltd.  
<TEXT>
 &UR; (Distributed by the New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
<P>
   (UNDATED) _ America's House of Representatives voted last month
to phase out the country's estate tax over the next ten years.
</P>
<P>
   If the law passes the Senate and has enough support to override
