<HEADLINE>
SHOULD ESTATE TAXES BE ABOLISHED?  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Financial Editors...NOTE 200-word trim)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist. Nonsubscribers
can use this article only by special arrangement. For purchase
