<P>
   SCI-ARCTIC-ICE (Oslo, Norway) _ Melting Arctic caps may yield
environmental disaster, but have some economic benefits. Scientist
theorize the extent of the damage and the future of the caps and
explore a new theory in which the caps melt each summer. By Walter
Gibbs. (1347 words)
</P>
