<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-10 15:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7989 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a BC-SCI-WATCH-NYT &LR;      07-10 0662
