Davidians' conversations moments before the compound was consumed
by flames. In the tapes, those speaking can be heard to say ``pour
the fuel'' and ``light the fire,'' lawyers for the government
contend, indicating that the cult followers _ not government agents
_ caused a deadly fire. By JIM HENDERSON.
</P>
