brilliant blooms flopping all over one another in a carefully
choreographed but artless-appearing display. What I had was London
</P>
<P>
   after the blitz. (Schuett, Cox News Service) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   LANE-COLUMN _ DAYTONA BEACH, Fla. _ Forget what they say on the
Sunday morning news shows. The key to understanding this years
elections is The Boredom Factor. This presidential election is
going to see record levels of voter absenteeism. Levels that go
beyond apathy into something resembling a voter boycott. This is a
strange year. For the first time there was more suspense in the
Mexican presidential race than in the American. Lane, Daytona Beach
News-Journal) MOVED.
</P>
