<P>
   LOW-POWER-RADIO (Washington) _ The FCC and Republicans in
Congress have been fighting for months over the commission's plan
to license thousands of low-power radio stations. And now the first
batch of applicants for the spectrum have come in. By David
Leonhardt.
</P>
