<P>
   GREGG-BIOTECH (Undated) _ A last-minute effort by N.H. Senator
Judd Gregg to extend a lucrative biotechnology patent held by
Columbia University, his alma mater, is running into a storm of
criticsm from drug manufacturers, consumer groups and members of
Congress. By Ronald Rosenberg. 1500 words.
</P>
<P>
