<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-10 20:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8379 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r p BC-HILLARY-CLINTON-HNS &LR;      07-10 0825
