 PERSONALS: `Survivor' Versus the Nation 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (Eds: This story also moved in the ``l'' lifestyle news
file.) &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; By LEAH GARCHIK &QC;  &LR; 
 &UR; c.2000, San Francisco Chronicle &LR;  &QC; 
 &QL; 
_ ``The Early Show'' has been devoting two full segments every
Thursday morning to discussions of ``Survivor,'' notes the Nation,
which also reports that local TV stations give the presidential
race an average of 39 seconds a night.
</P>
