</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PHOTO:
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service
Macintosh graphics files that moved Monday, 07/10/00. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been posted
on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST_Peace talks -- 2 x 8 -- (BC-MIDEAST-ISSUES-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   RACE_Two questions -- 11p x 4 -- (BC-RACE-POLL-NYT)
</P>
<P>
